'''Open Source Parking'''


URL = http://www.opensourceparking.com/

OpenSourceParking.com is a domain parking service that helps Free Software and Open Source. Domain parking provides a place-holder web page for an undeveloped domain name.

"The project's goals are to increase the market share for open source software and generate revenue from advertising on the parked domains, which will be used to fund "political and promotional efforts" on behalf of open source software."
([http://news.netcraft.com/archives/2006/04/17/perens_launches_open_source_domain_parking_service.html])


